--- Auditor should only see anonymized summaries, not full holding details.
--- The current design leaks counterparty identity and exact amounts to the auditor.
+-- Separate contract with minimal disclosure for auditor
+template AuditRecord
+  with
+    custodian : Party
+    auditor : Party
+    reference : Text
+    eventType : Text
+  where
+    signatory custodian
+    observer auditor
